OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,FAndy Burnham is "extremely liberal",
OL,7,FDonald Trump has said in his first
OL,8,Fpublic comments about the former
OL,9,FGreater Manchester mayor since he
OL,10,Femerged as the frontrunner to replace
OL,11,FSir Keir Starmer.
OL,13,FThe US president told reporters Mr
OL,14,FBurnham "probably won't open up the
OL,15,FNorth Sea" for oil exploration, and
OL,16,Fthat "the UK is dying", signalling
OL,17,Fthat the Labour MP could be facing a
OL,18,Frocky relationship with Mr Trump.
OL,26,@nD@QOUnD@cO]vD@IOUwD@JO]xD@FOUxD@VO]
