OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,FThe Makerfield MP has been critical of
OL,7,FMr Trump in the past, describing
OL,8,FAmerican politics as "polarised" and
OL,9,F"poisonous" while on the campaign
OL,10,Ftrail in June.
OL,12,FAs rioters stormed the US Capitol in
OL,13,F2021, Mr Burnham posted on X: "Any UK
OL,14,Fpolitician who gave Trump the time of
OL,15,Fday should be ashamed right now."
OL,17,FAsked at the White House what he knew
OL,18,Fabout Mr Burnham, Mr Trump said: "I
OL,19,Fdon't know, I think I see that he was,
OL,20,FI guess, the mayor of a town.
OL,26,@pD@VOUpD@`O]qD@AOUqD@KO]uD@_OUwD@aO]zD@
