OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,F"I hear he's extremely liberal,
OL,7,Fextremely, so that means he probably
OL,8,Fwon't open up the North Sea."
OL,10,FPrime Minister Sir Keir sought to
OL,11,Fpursue a conciliatory approach and
OL,12,Finitially even drew praise for his
OL,13,Fdeft handling of the unpredictable
OL,14,Fpresident, but their relationship
OL,15,Fdeteriorated over the Iran conflict.
OL,17,FMr Burnham's route to Number 10
OL,18,Fappears wide open, with few other
OL,19,FLabour MPs being discussed as
OL,20,Fpotential challengers.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@]O]
