OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,FBut former armed forces minister Al
OL,7,FCarns, who resigned earlier this month
OL,8,Fin a row over defence spending,
OL,9,Fremains a possible contender, calling
OL,10,Ffor a "proper debate" on the country's
OL,11,Ffuture.
OL,26,@rD@GOUrD@UO]
