OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,FHe stopped short of saying he would
OL,7,Fchallenge for the Labour leadership,
OL,8,Fbut posting on X he set out "tests"
OL,9,Fthat any contender should meet,
OL,10,Fincluding spending 3% of GDP on
OL,11,Fdefence, fixing the crisis with youth
OL,12,Funemployment, adding a trillion pounds
OL,13,Fto UK GDP within the next decade and
OL,14,Fimproving the UK's energy
OL,15,Finfrastructure.
OL,17,FMr Carns concluded: "None of this is
OL,18,Fcomplicated."
OL,26,@pD@]OUpD@cO]yD@UOUzD@MO]
