OL,3,CDonald Trump on Andy Burnham: 'I hear
OL,4,Che's extremely liberal, extremely'
OL,6,FMr Burnham is reportedly still
OL,7,Fconsidering who to choose for the role.
OL,9,FA temporary VAT cut to reduce prices
OL,10,Fat family attractions such as zoos and
OL,11,Ftheme parks as well as the cost of
OL,12,Fchildren's cinema tickets and
OL,13,Frestaurant meals is set to come into
OL,14,Feffect on Thursday after Ms Reeves
OL,15,Fannounced the "Great British Summer
OL,16,FSavings" measure.
